%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aretha%20Franklin's%20sons%20awarded%20valuable%20property%20after%20the%20singer's%20handwritten%20will%2C%20signed%20with%20a%20smiley%20face%2C%20discovered%20hidden%20in%20a%20couch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aretha%20Franklin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5b71484742e1cc3674518b48%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAretha%20Franklin%20performs%20onstage%20at%20the%20Elton%20John%20AIDS%20Foundation%20Commemorates%20Its%2025th%20Year%20And%20Honors%20Founder%20Sir%20Elton%20John%20During%20New%20York%20Fall%20Gala%20at%20Cathedral%20of%20St.%20John%20the%20Divine%20on%20November%207%2C%202017%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3Cp%3EDimitrios%20Kambouris%20%2F%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20will%20of%20Aretha%20Franklin%2C%20who%20died%20in%202018%2C%20has%20been%20disputed%20after%20two%20versions%20emerged.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20newer%20one%2C%20dated%202014%2C%20was%20found%20buried%20in%20a%20couch.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20recent%20court%20decision%20has%20granted%20ownership%20of%20her%20former%20homes%20to%20her%20sons.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faretha-franklin-has-died-at-age-76-publicist-says-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAretha%20Franklin%2C%20the%20American%20%26quot%3BQueen%20of%20Soul%2C%26quot%3B%20passed%3C%2Fa%3E%20away%20in%20Detroit%20in%202018.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20it%20was%20believed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faretha-franklin-reportedly-died-without-a-will-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe%20had%20left%20no%20will%20behind%3C%2Fa%3E%20relating%20to%20her%20fortune%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Faretha-franklin-net-worth-demanded-to-be-paid-in-cash-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enet%20worth%20of%20%2480%20million%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20legal%20battle%20arose%20after%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Faretha-franklin-dead-celebrities-reactions-twitter-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeath%20from%20pancreatic%20cancer%20aged%2078%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20a%20will%20was%20not%20initially%20recovered.%20However%2C%20her%20niece%20Sabrina%20Owens%2C%20the%20estate's%20executor%20at%20the%20time%2C%20discovered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-67565918%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20handwritten%20sets%20of%20documents%20nine%20months%20later%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Franklin's%20Detroit%20home%2C%20the%20BBC%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20version%20Owens%20found%2C%20dated%202010%2C%20has%20been%20superseded%20by%20a%20recently-discovered%20will%20from%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20newer%20will%20was%20discovered%20wedged%20between%20couch%20cushions.%20A%20recent%20court%20decision%20on%20the%20competing%20documents%20granted%20her%20sons%20ownership%20of%20her%20former%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20by%20%3Cspan%3EJudge%20Jennifer%20Callaghan%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ewas%20delivered%20four%20months%20after%20a%20D%3Cspan%3Eetroit-area%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ejury%20deemed%20the%20document%20valid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFranklin%20signed%20The%20will%20with%20a%20smiley-face%20signature%20inside%20the%20letter%20%26quot%3BA.%26quot%3B%20The%20papers%2C%20dating%20back%20to%202014%2C%20override%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhandwritten-wills-shake-up-aretha-franklins-estate-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehandwritten%20will%20from%202010%20discovered%20at%20Franklin's%20Detroit%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019%2C%20according%20to%20the%20presiding%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%202014%20document%20implies%20the%20music%20icon's%20desire%20for%20her%20youngest%20son%20to%20assume%20control%20over%20her%20estate.%20Kecalf%20and%20his%20children%20are%20now%20set%20to%20inherit%20Franklin's%20gated%20mansion%20in%20suburban%20Detroit%2C%20initially%20valued%20at%20%241.1%20million%20in%202018%20and%20considered%20the%20%26quot%3Bcrown%20jewel%26quot%3B%20of%20her%20real%20estate%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20son%20Ted%20White%20II%2C%20who%20favored%20the%202010%20will%2C%20was%20awarded%20a%20separate%20house%20in%20Detroit%2C%20although%20it%20had%20already%20been%20sold%20for%20%24300%2C000%20before%20the%20competing%20wills%20emerged.%20His%20lawyer%20mentioned%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20is%20seeking%20the%20sale%20proceeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20third%20son%2C%20Edward%20Franklin%2C%20was%20granted%20another%20property%20under%20the%202014%20will%20by%20Judge%20Callaghan.%20The%20fate%20of%20Franklin's%20fourth%20home%2C%20valued%20at%20over%20%241%20million%2C%20remains%20undecided%2C%20with%20the%20judge%20stating%20that%20the%202014%20will%20did%20not%20specify%20the%20recipient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20significant%20step%20forward.%20We've%20narrowed%20the%20remaining%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Charles%20McKelvie%2C%20an%20attorney%20for%20Kecalf%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20both%20documents%20indicated%20Franklin's%20desire%20for%20her%20four%20sons%20to%20split%20the%20income%20from%20her%20music%20and%20copyrights%2C%20discrepancies%20existed.%20The%202014%20will%20suggested%20Kecalf's%20inheritance%20of%20the%20%241.1%20million%20home%2C%20while%20the%202010%20will%20divided%20assets%20more%20evenly%20among%20her%20heirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20trial%2C%20Kecalf%20testified%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Faretha-franklin-purse-paid-in-cash-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehis%20mother%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20conducted%20business%20on%20the%20couch%2C%20making%20it%20plausible%20for%20a%20will%20to%20be%20found%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20jury%20ruled%20in%20favor%20of%20the%202014%20will%2C%20considering%20it%20superior%20to%20the%202010%20document.%20Franklin's%20eldest%20child%2C%20Clarence%2C%20who%20was%20not%20part%20of%20the%20dispute%2C%20will%20receive%20an%20undisclosed%20percentage%20of%20the%20estate%20per%20a%20pre-trial%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20dispute%20persists%20over%20how%20to%20handle%20Franklin's%20music%20assets.%20A%20status%20conference%20with%20the%20judge%20is%20scheduled%20for%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faretha-franklins-sons-awarded-properties-after-will-found-in-couch%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701514450000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656b0b7f0ec98e92f74b771a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faretha-franklins-sons-awarded-properties-after-will-found-in-couch%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%202014%20will%20signed%20with%20a%20smiley%20face%20by%20Aretha%20Franklin%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BQueen%20of%20Soul%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20found%20wedged%20between%20couch%20cushions%2C%20challenging%20a%20previous%20will.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99%3A%20Hunger%2C%20Inequity%20and%20a%20%2430-Trillion%20Economy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F13084433%2FIMG_1352.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20goes%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1980689%5C%22%3EPress%20Information%20Bureau%20(PIB)%20note%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20on%2029%20November%2C%202023%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Cabinet%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20decided%20that%20the%20Central%20government%20will%20provide%20free%20food%20grains%20to%20about%2081.35%20crore%20beneficiaries%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Garib%20Kalyan%20Anna%20Yojana%20(PMGKAY)%20for%20a%20period%20of%20five%20years%20with%20effect%20from%201st%20January%2C%202024%E2%80%A6%20This%20is%20a%20historic%20decision%20that%20places%20PMGKAY%20amongst%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20social%20welfare%20schemes%20aimed%20at%20ensuring%20food%20and%20nutrition%20security%20for%2081.35%20crore%20persons%2C%20at%20an%20estimated%20cost%20of%20Rs.%2011.80%20lakh%20crore%20over%20a%205-year%20period%E2%80%A6%20The%20decision%20reflects%20the%20strong%20commitment%20of%20Hon.%20PM%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%20towards%20efficient%20and%20targeted%20welfare%20through%20fulfilment%20of%20basic%20food%20and%20nutrition%20requirements%20of%20the%20population.%20Ensuring%20food%20security%20at%20this%20scale%20during%20Amrit%20Kaal%20would%20play%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20dedicating%20efforts%20towards%20building%20an%20aspirational%20and%20developed%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20suo%20motto%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Fchhattisgarh-assembly%2Fpm-modi-attacks-chhattisgarh-cm-cong-over-betting-app-row-says-they-didnt-even-spare-name-of-mahadev%2Farticle67497413.ece%5C%22%3Eproclaimed%20this%20largesse%20at%20an%20election%20rally%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20November%204%20this%20year.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20poor%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20of%20the%20country%20from%20the%20land%20of%20Durg%20(Chhattisgarh)%20that%20I%20have%20decided%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20will%20now%20extend%20the%20PMGKAY%20providing%20free%20ration%20to%2080%20crore%20poor%20people%20of%20the%20country%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years.%E2%80%9D%20He%20claimed%20that%20he%20himself%20came%20from%20a%20poor%20family%20and%20he%20considers%20poor%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbiggest%20caste%20%5Bgroup%5D%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scheme%20involves%20free%20supply%20of%20five%20kg%20of%20food%20grains%20per%20month%20to%20over%20810%20million%20people%20who%20account%20for%20three-fourths%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20rural%20and%20half%20of%20the%20urban%20population.%20The%20scheme%20was%20initiated%20by%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%20in%202013%20under%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%20to%20provide%20subsidised%20food-grains%20to%20the%20poor.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20gone%20through%20changes%20since%20and%20the%20Modi%20government%20introduced%20the%20PMGKAY%20in%202020%20as%20a%20free%20ration%20entitlement%20scheme.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fmodi-amrit-kaal-hunger-unemployment%5C%22%3EHunger%20and%20Unemployment%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Amrit%20Kaal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fopinion%2Feditorial%2Fadmission-of-failure-to-reduce-poverty-hunger-2761143%5C%22%3Eextended%20for%20one%20year%20in%20December%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20country%20was%20recovering%20from%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20and%20has%20been%20kept%20going%20with%20short%20extensions%20since.%20It%20is%20this%20scheme%20which%20is%20now%20being%20extended%20by%20five%20more%20years%20confirming%20the%20fact%20that%20majority%20of%20Indians%20are%20so%20poor%20that%20they%20cannot%20even%20afford%20to%20buy%20food%2C%20which%20is%20a%20basic%20necessity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20deep%20deprivation%20has%20accelerated%20during%20the%20NDA%20regime%20headed%20by%20Modi%20if%20one%20goes%20by%20the%20Gallup%20World%20Poll%20survey%20for%20India%20focusing%20on%20lack%20of%20money%20to%20buy%20food.%20The%20period%20covered%20in%20the%20study%20is%202018%20to%202021.%20About%2040.2%25%20of%20respondents%20in%20the%20survey%20reported%20not%20having%20enough%20money%20for%20food%20in%202018.%20This%20rose%20to%2048%25%20in%202021.%20In%202023%20it%20seemed%20to%20have%20climbed%20up%20further%20compelling%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sarkariallexams.in%2Fworld-news%2Fa-narrative-of-roti-kapada-aur-makaan-under-the-nda%2F-%5C%22%3Eextend%20the%20%E2%80%98free-ration%E2%80%99%20scheme%20to%20over%20half%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20five%20more%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20abject%20poverty%20is%20further%20evidenced%20by%20the%202023%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20(GHI)%2C%20wherein%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalhungerindex.org%2Findia.html%5C%22%3EIndia%20ranks%20111th%20out%20of%20the%20125%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20a%20score%20of%2028.7%20in%20the%202023%20GHI%2C%20India%20has%20a%20level%20of%20hunger%20that%20is%20serious.%20GHI%20is%20a%20peer-reviewed%20report%2C%20published%20on%20an%20annual%20basis%20by%20Concern%20Worldwide%20and%20Welthungerhilfe.%20The%20GHI%20is%20a%20tool%20designed%20to%20comprehensively%20measure%20and%20track%20hunger%20at%20global%2C%20regional%2C%20and%20national%20levels%2C%20reflecting%20multiple%20dimensions%20of%20hunger%20over%20time.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20aims%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20understanding%20of%20the%20struggle%20against%20hunger%2C%20provide%20a%20way%20to%20compare%20levels%20of%20hunger%20between%20countries%20and%20regions%2C%20and%20call%20attention%20to%20those%20areas%20of%20the%20world%20where%20hunger%20levels%20are%20highest%20and%20where%20the%20need%20for%20additional%20efforts%20to%20eliminate%20hunger%20is%20greatest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fformer-rbi-governor-raghuram-rajan-on-indias-economic-future%5C%22%3EFormer%20RBI%20Governor%20Raghuram%20Rajan%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20Economic%20Future%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20distressing%20is%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20low-income%20levels%20and%20deprivation%20is%20accompanied%20by%20it%20being%20among%20the%20most%20inequitable%20countries%20in%20the%20world%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Findias-richest-1-own-more-than-40-of-total-wealth-oxfam%2Farticle66381944.ece%5C%22%3Ethe%20richest%201%25%20owning%20more%20than%2040%25%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20total%20wealth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20the%20bottom%20half%20of%20the%20population%20together%20share%20just%203%25.%C2%A0%20Reality%20is%20that%20the%20rich%20are%20getting%20richer%20while%20the%20poor%20are%20getting%20poorer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20in%20this%20canvas%20that%20a%20near%20ten-fold%20increase%20in%20the%20size%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20per-capita%20GDP%20is%20being%20projected%20to%20be%20achieved%20in%20the%20next%2025%20years.%20NITI%20Aayog%20recently%20announced%20the%20draft%20of%20the%20vision%20document%20%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat%20%40%202047%E2%80%99%20to%20make%20India%20a%20%2430%20trillion%20economy%20by%202047%20with%20a%20per%20capita%20GDP%20of%20%2417%2C590%20would%20be%20ready%20by%20December%2C%202023.%C2%A0%20America%E2%80%99s%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group%20would%20be%20readying%20this%20document%20in%20consultation%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Fvision-document-to-make-india-a-30-trillion-economy-by-2047-in-final-stages-draft-to-be-ready-by-december-9005032%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cbusiness%20tycoons%20and%20corporate%20honchos%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20and%20Gautam%20Adani.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENITI%20Aayog%20CEO%20BVR%20Subrahmanyam%20said%20that%20ten%20sectoral%20groups%20of%20secretaries%20from%20various%20ministries%20created%20around%20themes%20including%20infrastructure%2C%20welfare%2C%20commerce%20and%20industry%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20governance%20have%20each%20prepared%20a%20vision%20document%20in%20a%20process%20that%20lasted%20nearly%20two%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20claimed%20that%20the%20Indian%20economy%20is%20currently%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20fifth%20largest%2C%20with%20a%20size%20of%20%243.75%20trillion.%20The%20annual%20per-capita%20income%2C%20as%20per%20the%20government%20data%2C%20stood%20at%20%E2%82%B998%2C374%20in%202022-23%20i.e.%2C%20%241%2C183.%20Atanu%20Chakraborty%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20HDFC%20Bank%20expects%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Feconomy%2Findia-to-be-30-trillion-economy-by-2050-with-per-capita-income-of-21-000-hdfc-bank-chief-atanu-chakraborty-11697031442896.html%5C%22%3Ethe%20Indian%20economy%20to%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20in%20the%20next%20four%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20reach%20the%20%2430%20trillion-mark%20by%202050%2C%20with%20the%20per-capita%20income%20soaring%20to%20%2421%2C000%20by%20then.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBusiness%20tycoon%20Gautam%20Adani%20is%20more%20assertive%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adani.com%2Fblogs%2Findia-on-track-to-becoming-a-25-trillion30-trillion-economy-by-2050-says-gautam-adani%5C%22%3Echips%20in%20with%20this%20gem%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9CFollowing%20independence%2C%20it%20took%20us%2058%20years%20to%20get%20to%20our%20first%20trillion%20dollars%20of%20GDP%2C%2012%20years%20to%20get%20to%20the%20next%20trillion%20and%20just%205%20years%20for%20the%20third%20trillion.%20I%20anticipate%20that%20within%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20India%20will%20start%20adding%20a%20trillion%20dollars%20to%20its%20GDP%20every%2018%20months.%20This%20puts%20us%20on%20track%20to%20be%20a%20%2425-%2430%20trillion%20economy%20by%202050%20and%20drive%20India%E2%80%99s%20stock%20market%20capitalisation%20to%20over%20%2440%20trillion.%E2%80%9D%20And%20he%20adds%20to%20good%20measure%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20country%20is%20now%20the%20most%20exciting%20land%20of%20opportunities%E2%80%9D%20Indeed%2C%20he%20knows%20better!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20realise%20this%20dream%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Fvision-document-to-make-india-a-30-trillion-economy-by-2047-in-final-stages-draft-to-be-ready-by-december-9005032%2F%5C%22%3ENITI%20Aayog%E2%80%99s%20Subrahmanyam%20advocates%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Fvision-document-to-make-india-a-30-trillion-economy-by-2047-in-final-stages-draft-to-be-ready-by-december-9005032%2F%5C%22%3Edrastic%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9C..2047%20will%20be%20a%20very%20different%20India.%20It%20will%20be%20highly%20urbanised.%20Where%20we%20live%2C%20the%20way%20we%20move%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20jobs%20we%20do%2C%20what%20we%20eat%E2%80%93things%20are%20going%20to%20change%20massively%20by%20that%20time%E2%80%A6%20The%20government%20needs%20radical%20restructuring%2C%20both%20horizontally%20and%20vertically%2C%20such%20that%20the%20lower%20levels%20of%20government%20be%20entirely%20tasked%20with%20implementation%20so%20that%20senior%20officials%20can%20spend%20more%20time%20ideating.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20pray%2C%20what%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdevelopment%20model%E2%80%9D%20to%20achieve%20this%20mammoth%20task%3F%20Predatory%20or%20participatory%3F%20In%20December%20of%202020%2C%20Subrahmanyam%E2%80%99s%20illustrious%20predecessor%20Amitabh%20Kant%20laid%20bare%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freclaimtherepublic.in%2F2021%2F11%2F30%2Fprivatisation-an-affront-to-the-indian-constitution%2F%5C%22%3Eoligarchic-cum-monopolistic%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20promoting%20select%20champions%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20India%20a%20government%20has%20thought%20big%20in%20terms%20of%20size%20and%20scale%20and%20said%20we%20want%20to%20produce%20global%20champions.%20Nobody%20had%20the%20political%20will%20and%20the%20courage%20to%20say%20that%20we%20want%20to%20support%20five%20companies%20who%20want%20to%20be%20global%20champions.%E2%80%9D%20As%20the%20Adani%20story%20unfolds%2C%20we%20see%20this%20model%20being%20practiced%20with%20vengeance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20this%20model%20while%20hunger%20and%20extreme%20inequality%20persists%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20%2430%20trillion%20will%20go%20to%20one%20to%20two%20percent%20of%20the%20population%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20economy%20would%20look%20like%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20drunken%20stunted%20dog%E2%80%9D%20as%20described%20in%20Aseem%20Shrivastava%20and%20Ashish%20Kothari%E2%80%99s%20book%20%3Cem%3EChurning%20the%20Earth%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CImagine%20a%20puppy%20which%20is%20fed%20a%20special%20kind%20of%20diet%20which%20distorts%20his%20growth%20so%20that%20one%20of%20his%20legs%20grows%20astonishingly%20fast%2C%20while%20the%20other%20three%20get%20stunted%20to%20various%20degrees.%20Now%20imagine%20that%20the%20puppy%20grows%20into%20a%20dog%20of%20sorts%2C%20gets%20drunk%20and%20begin%20to%20spin%20around%20the%20house%20in%20ecstasy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20wonder%20whether%20this%20is%20the%20fate%20of%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99%20in%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99%20which%20the%20PIB%20note%20is%20talking%20about.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fm-g-devasahayam-2%5C%22%3EM.G.%20Devasahayam%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20former%20Army%20and%20IAS%20officer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701514080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Findias-amrit-kaal-hunger-inequity-and-a-30-trillion-economy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20near%20ten-fold%20increase%20in