0Modi%20Holds%20Talks%20with%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02160923%2FEffect-9.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20COP%20summit%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20a%20series%20of%20discussions%20with%20world%20leaders%20ranging%20from%20his%20introductory%20meeting%20with%20the%20newly%20elected%20Maldivian%20president%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20to%20the%20first%20high-level%20interaction%20with%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20President%20Isaac%20Herzog%20after%20the%20October%207%20terror%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20interaction%2C%20Modi%20met%20with%20the%20Maldivian%20President%20in%20Dubai%20on%20Friday%2C%20two%20weeks%20after%20Muizzu%20won%20the%20presidential%20election.%20The%20meeting%20also%20took%20place%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Maldives%20government%20asking%20India%20to%20withdraw%20Indian%20defence%20personnel%20who%20were%20stationed%20to%20operate%20choppers%2C%20a%20day%20after%20Muizzu%20was%20sworn%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20island%20nation%E2%80%99s%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20outcome%20of%20the%20meeting%20was%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccore%20group%E2%80%9D%20as%20per%20India%20or%20a%20%E2%80%9Chigh%20level%20committee%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Maldives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20press%20note%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37325%2FPrime_Ministers_meeting_with_the_President_of_the_Republic_of_the_Maldives%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%20%E2%80%9Cdiscussed%20ways%20to%20further%20deepen%20their%20partnership%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccore%20group%E2%80%9D%20was%20a%20result%20of%20this%20direction%20of%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldivian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpresidency.gov.mv%2FPress%2FArticle%2F29241%5C%22%3Epress%20communique%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20declared%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Chigh%20level%20committee%E2%80%9D%20would%20be%20looking%20to%20enhance%20development%20and%20economic%20cooperation%2C%20people-to-people%20contacts%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fpresidencymv%2Fstatus%2F1730636900619481225%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Etweet%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Maldivian%20president%E2%80%99s%20office%20said%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%20%E2%80%9Cdiscussed%20cooperation%20between%20the%20Maldives%20and%20India%20on%20matters%20of%20concern%20and%20sensitivities%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Maldives%20and%20of%20mutual%20benefit%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20two%20countries%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2C%20however%2C%20no%20more%20details%20about%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20group%20or%20its%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20key%20meeting%20was%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20talks%20with%20Israeli%20President%20Isaac%20Herzog.%20While%20Modi%20has%20spoken%20with%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20this%20was%20the%20highest-level%20meeting%20between%20India%20and%20Israel%20since%20Hamas%20launched%20a%20terror%20attack%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20an%20MEA%20readout%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20exchanged%20views%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Congoing%20Israel%20%E2%80%93%20Hamas%20conflict%20in%20the%20region%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20expressed%20his%20condolences%20on%20the%20loss%20of%20lives%20in%20the%20October%207%20terror%20attacks%20and%20welcomed%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20reportedly%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20need%20for%20continued%20and%20safe%20delivery%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%20for%20the%20affected%20population%E2%80%9D%20and%20recalled%20India%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctwo-state%20solution%E2%80%9D