f%20community%20health%20and%20wellbeing%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Queensland%2C%20Australia%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20because%20high%20cholesterol%20can%20lead%20to%20cardiovascular%20problems%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fheart-attack-signs-symptoms-chest-pain-short-breath-tired-nausea-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20strokes%20and%20mini%20strokes%2C%20narrow%20arteries%2C%20and%20peripheral%20arterial%20disease%2C%20which%20is%20when%20a%20build-up%20of%20fatty%20deposits%20in%20the%20arteries%20restricts%20blood%20supply%20to%20the%20legs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fdash-diet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20be%20the%20first%20port%20of%20call%20for%20lowering%20cholesterol%2C%20and%20those%20looking%20to%20improve%20their%20heart%20health%20might%20want%20to%20speak%20to%20a%20dietitian%20for%20individual%20support%2C%20Ball%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20eating%20more%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20is%20a%20good%20place%20to%20start%2C%20because%20they%20are%20a%20good%20source%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Ffiber-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiber%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20known%20to%20reduce%20LDL%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Bbad%2C%26quot%3B%20cholesterol%2C%20she%20said.%20The%20FDA%20recommends%20people%20get%20a%20minimum%20of%2028g%20of%20fiber%20per%20day%2C%20and%20whole%20grains%2C%20oats%2C%20and%20beans%20are%20also%20good%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20has%20also%20shown%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsupplements-you-should-or-should-not-take-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupplements%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20significantly%20lower%20cholesterol%20levels.%20Ball%20shared%20the%20two%20supplements