20impairing%20democratic%20discourse%20forever%2C%20pushing%20a%20marketplace%20of%20free%20ideas%20to%20the%20point%20of%20collapse%20under%20the%20immense%20weight%20of%20fake%20stories.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20noted%20with%20concern%20that%20a%20cursory%20glance%20at%20newspapers%20every%20day%20brings%20to%20the%20fore%20communal%20and%20vigilante%20violence%20resulting%20out%20of%20rumuors%20and%20disinformation%20campaigns.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20that%20while%20the%20country%20was%20faced%20with%20the%20tragic%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20the%20internet%20was%20rife%20with%20the%20most%20outrageous%20fake%20news%20and%20rumours%20%E2%80%93%20a%20source%20of%20comic%20relief%20in%20difficult%20times%2C%20but%20also%20forcing%20us%20to%20rethink%20the%20limits%20of%20free%20speech%20on%20the%20internet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20underlined%20that%20privacy%20in%20the%20digital%20age%20is%20not%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20data%20protection%20but%20it%20is%20a%20fundamental%20right%2C%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20must%20actively%20champion%E2%80%9D.%20While%20noting%20that%20the%20judiciary%20globally%20is%20facing%20challenges%20from%20technological%20advancements%20vis-a-vis%20protecting%20privacy%2C%20he%20said%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20develop%20legal%20frameworks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20while%20noting%20that%20Facial%20Recognition%20Technology%20(FRT)%20represented%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmarvel%20of%20technological%20innovation%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said%20its%20application%20raises%20significant%20privacy%20and%20discrimination%20concerns.%20%E2%80%9CStudies%20reveal%20inherent%20biases%20within%20FRT%20algorithms%2C%20especially%20in%20identifying%20darker-skinned%20women%2C%20ethnic%20minorities%2C%20and%20transgender%20individuals.%20The%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20accentuated%20these%20concerns%20with%20controversies%20surrounding%20FRT%E2%80%99s%20use%20in%20health%20data%20management.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asserted%20all%20individuals%20irrespective%20of%20their%20socio-economic%20status%20are%20deeply%20affected%20by%20violations%20of%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%2C%20autonomy%20and%20intimacy%20while%20dismissing%20the%20notion%20that%20economic%20status%20and%20access%20to%20welfare%20entitlements%20are%20more%20important%20than%20civil%20and%20political%20rights%20for%20socio-economically%20disadvantaged%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701510028000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F02154727%2FScreenshot-2022-11-02-at-3.45.44-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffake-news-drowns-out-true-information-impairs-democratic-discourse-cji-chandrachud%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delivering%20Justice%20V.M.%20Tarkunde%20Memorial%20Lecture%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Friday%2C%20he%20dismissed%20the%20notion%20that%20economic%20status%20and%20access%20to%20welfare%20entitlements%20are%20more%20important%20than%20civil%20and%20political%20rights%20for%20socio-economically%20disadvantaged%20communities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffake-news-drowns-out-true-information-impairs-democratic-discourse-cji-chandrachud%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tihar%20Jail%20Terminates%2050%20Employees%20After%20Biometric%20Mismatch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Tihar%20Jail%20administration%20has%20served%20termination%20notice%20to%20its%2050%20employees%20after%20a%20verification%20drive%20found%20a%20mismatch%20in%20their%20biometric%20identification%20records%2C%20officials%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Tihar%20Jail%20administration%2C%20among%20these%2050%20terminated%20employees%2C%2039%20are%20warders%2C%209%20are%20assistant%20superintendent%20and%202%20are%20matron.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20was%20served%20as%20per%20the%20directi