ctacular%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleonids-2023-when-how-to-watch-meteor-shower-shooting-stars-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeteor%20shower%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20year%20is%20fast%20approaching%2C%20and%20it'll%20be%20a%20particularly%20exceptional%20one%20you%20won't%20want%20to%20miss.%20Here's%20how%20and%20when%20to%20see%20the%20Geminid%20meteor%20shower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Geminids%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20and%20most%20reliable%20annual%20meteor%20showers%2C%20happening%20every%20year%20in%20mid-December%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.nasa.gov%2Fsolar-system%2Fmeteors-meteorites%2Fgeminids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20NASA%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20meteor%20showers%20come%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdevil-comet-excites-scientists-as-it-passes-through-solar-system-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomet%20debris%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Geminids%20come%20from%20a%20large%20asteroid-like%20object%20called%203200%20Phaethon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhen%20to%20see%20the%20Geminid%20meteor%20shower%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-watch-geminids-meteor-shower-colorful-shooting-stars-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGeminids%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20peak%20on%20the%20night%20of%20December%2013%20and%20into%20the%20early%20morning%20hours%20of%20December%2014%2C%20Bill%20Cooke%2C%20lead%20of%20NASA's%20Meteoroid%20Environments%20Office%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStar%20gazers%20in%20the%20Northern%20Hemisphere%20should%20be%20able%20to%20spot%20the%20spectacular%20display%20as%20early%20as%209%20p.m.%20or%2010%20p.m.%20local%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.nasa.gov%2Fskywatching%2Fwhats-up%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20NASA%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20just%20northerners%20who%20get%20to%20view%20the%20showers%20%E2%80%94%20they'll%20be%20visible%20in%20the%20night%20sky%20worldwide%2C%20per%20NASA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20showers%20this%20year%20will%20be%20particularly%20brilliant%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.nasa.gov%2FWatch_the_Skies%2Ftag%2Fgeminids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emuch%20better%20than%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20because%20the%20moon%20will%20only%20be%201%25%20illuminated%20on%20the%20night%20of%20Dec.%2013%2C%20Cooke%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20moonlight%20interfering%2C%20Cooke%20said%2C%20you%20should%20see%20a%20Geminid%20about%20one%20to%20every%20two%20minutes%20on%20the%20peak%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20gonna%20be%20a%20very%20good%20year%20for%20the%20Geminids%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooke%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20year%20of%20the%20Geminids.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhere%20to%20see%20the%20Geminid%20meteor%20shower%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20best%20view%20of%20the%20showers%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20go%20outside%20somewhere%20away%20from%20city%20lights%20and%20street%20lights%2C%20according%20to%20NASA.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdarkest-skies-by-state-watch-space-events-stargazing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edarker%20the%20sky%2C%20the%20better%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLie%20flat%20on%20your%20back%20with%20your%20feet%20facing%20south%20and%20look%20up%2C%20taking%20in%20as%20much%20of%20the%20sky%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.nasa.gov%2Fsolar-system%2Fmeteors-meteorites%2Fgeminids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENASA%20suggests%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20about%2030%20minutes%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20your%20eyes%20will%20adapt%20and%20you%20will%20begin%20to%20see%20meteors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20probably%20want%20to%20bring%20a%20few%20bla