E%3Cu%3Emacros%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20for%20a%20short%20period%20can%20be%20beneficial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20calories%20determine%20if%20you%20lose%2C%20maintain%2C%20or%20gain%20weight%2C%20but%20the%20ratio%20of%20macronutrients%20you%20eat%20makes%20it%20easier%20or%20harder%20to%20stay%20in%20that%20calorie%20deficit%20without%20feeling%20hungry%2C%26quot%3B%20Turoff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20you%20could%20in%20theory%20eat%20only%20cookies%20and%20lose%20weight%20if%20you're%20in%20a%20calorie%20deficit%2C%20but%20you'd%20likely%20find%20yourself%20hungry%20so%20it%20would%20be%20hard%20to%20stick%20to%20the%20deficit%20(not%20to%20mention%20your%20health%20would%20suffer).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20reason%2C%20Turoff%20advises%20people%20looking%20to%20lose%20weight%20to%20start%20by%20getting%20a%20handle%20on%20calories%20before%20thinking%20about%20how%20much%20protein%20they're%20eating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chicken%20and%20vegetable%20pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656768c1fd6200867dd09ae0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221499%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20balanced%20meal%20incudes%20carbs%2C%20protein%2C%20fat%2C%20and%20fiber.%3Cp%3EJoff%20Lee%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EProtein%20is%20the%20most%20important%20macronutrient%20for%20most%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnless%20you're%20a%20professional%20bodybuilder%20or%20athlete%2C%20you%20probably%20don't%20need%20to%20worry%20too%20much%20about%20how%20many%20fats%20and%20carbs%20you're%20consuming%2C%20because%20the%20difference%20they%20can%20make%20is%20small.%20Protein%2C%20however%2C%20is%20worth%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20if%20you're%20trying%20to%20lose%20fat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20a%20numbers%20person%2C%20however%20I%20know%20that%20what's%20most%20important%20for%20fat%20loss%20and%20body%20composition