-cricketer-names-greatest-india-batter-its-not-sachin-tendulkar-or-virat-kohli-4626251%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chargesheet%20Filed%20Against%20AAP's%20Sanjay%20Singh%20In%20Delhi%20Liquor%20Policy%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20on%20Saturday%20filed%20a%2060-page%20chargesheet%20against%20AAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Delhi%20excise%20policy-linked%20money%20laundering%20case%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecution%20complaint%20has%20been%20filed%20before%20a%20local%20court%20under%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20supplementary%20chargesheet%20in%20this%20case%20as%20the%20agency%20had%20filed%20about%20five%20such%20complaints%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%2C%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20was%20arrested%20in%20this%20case%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20anti-money%20laundering%20agency%20had%20alleged%20that%20an%20accused%20businessman%20Dinesh%20Arora%20gave%20Rs%202%20crore%20in%20cash%20at%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP's%20residence%20in%20two%20tranches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20has%20rebutted%20the%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20MP%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20connection%20with%20its%20money%20laundering%20probe%20linked%20to%20the%202021-22%20Delhi%20Excise%20policy%20case%20and%20was%20the%20second%20high-profile%20leader%20after%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20a%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20to%20be%20held%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20that%20rules%20Delhi%20has%20called%20the%20arrests%20and%20the%20case%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20witch-hunt%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20investigation%20by%20the%20ED%20has%20revealed%20that%20Arora%20has%20given%20Rs%202%20crore%20cash%20at%20Singh's%20house%20on%20two%20occasions%20--%20Rs%20