diatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fkapil-sharma-and-sunil-grover-reunite-for-the-kapil-sharma-show-on-ott-as-they-end-the-6-year-long-fight-on-the-flight%2Farticleshow%2F105676021.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTrack%2C%20Hunt%2C%20Kill%26quot%3B%3A%20How%20Israel%20Plans%20To%20Destroy%20Hamas%20Leaders%20After%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20reportedly%20wants%20to%20follow%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20his%20predecessor%20Golda%20Meir%20and%20authorise%20an%20'Operation%20Wrath%20of%20God'-like%20mission%20--%20kill%20Israel's%20enemies%20across%20countries%2C%20spanning%20continents%20--%20once%20its%20campaign%20in%20Gaza%20winds%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-plans-to-kill-hamas-leaders-around-the-world-after-war%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Netanyahu%20has%20instructed%20Israel's%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20the%20Mossad%2C%20to%20streamline%20a%20plan%20to%20execute%20this%20task.%20Mossad%20is%20reportedly%20drawing%20up%20plans%20to%20neutralise%20high-value%20targets%20in%20Turkey%2C%20Lebanon%20and%20Qatar%20-%20the%20latter%20in%20particular%20as%20its%20capital%20plays%20host%20to%20a%20Hamas%20office.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas's%20political%20office%20was%20%26quot%3Bopened%20in%20Qatar%20in%202012%20in%20coordination%20with%20the%20United%20States%20government%2C%20following%20a%20US%20request%20to%20open%20a%20communication%20channel%26quot%3B%2C%20news%20agency%20AFP%20quoted%20a%20Qatari%20official%20in%20October.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Targets%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Mossad%20Director%20Efraim%20Halevy%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20operations%2C%20WSJ%20claims%2C%20warning%20that%20such%20actions%20could%20have%20unintended%20consequences%20and%20further%20destabilise%20the%20region.%20Halevy%20said%20eliminating%20Hamas%20targets%20across%20the%20globe%20would%20not%20necessarily%20eliminate%20threats%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPursuing%20Hamas%20on%20a%20worldwide%20scale%20and%20trying%20to%20systematically%20remove%20all%20its%20leaders%20from%20this%20world%20is%20a%20desire%20to%20exact%20revenge%2C%20not%20a%20desire%20to%20achieve%20a%20strategic%20aim%2C%26quot%3B%20Halevy%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20WSJ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20big%20names%20that%20may%20feature%20in%20Mossad's%20kill%20list%20are%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%2C%20Mohammed%20Deif%2C%20Yahya%20Sinwar%20and%20Khaled%20Mashal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIsmail%20Haniyeh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaniyeh%2C%2060%2C%20is%20a%20politician%20who%20is%20a%20former%20Palestinian%20prime%20minister.%20He%20was%20elected%20as%20the%20head%20of%20Hamas'%20political%20bureau%20in%202017.%20%C2%A0In%202006%2C%20while%20serving%20as%20the%20Palestinian%20PM%2C%20Haniyeh%20was%20the%20subject%20of%20an%20assassination%20plot%20using%20a%20poison-filled%20letter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaniyeh%20lives%20in%20voluntary%20exile%2C%20splitting%20his%20time%20between%20Qatar%20and%20Turkey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMohammed%20Deif%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeif%20heads%20Hamas'%20military%20wing%2C%20the%20Ezzdine%20al-Qassam%20Brigades%2C%20and%20is%20Israel's%20public%20enemy%20number%20one.%20Israeli%20authorities%20have%20tried%20to%20assassinate%20him%20at%20least%20six%20times%2C%20as%20per%20reports.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20on%20the%20US%20list%20of%20%26quot%3Binternational%20terrorists%26quot%3B%20since%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audio%20message%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BAl-Aqsa%20Flood%26quot%3B%2C%20carried%20Deif's%20voice.%20His%20current%20whereabouts%20are%20unknown%20but%20Israel%20believes%20he%20is%20fighting%20alongside%20Hamas%20fighters%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYahya%20Sinwar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinwar%2C%2061%2C%20is%20a%20former%20commander%20of%20the%20Ezzdine%20al-Qassam%20Brigades%20and%20was%20elected%20in%202017%20as%20head%20of%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza.%20He%20has%20spent%2023%20years%20in%20Israeli%20jails%20before%20his%20release%20in%202011%20in%20a%20prisoner%20exchange%20involving%20French-Israeli%20soldier%20Gilad%20Shalit%20who%20was%20held%20captive%20by%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20Israeli%20hostages%20taken%20to%20Gaza%20have%20spoken%20about%20encountering%20Sinwar%20during%20their%20captivity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKhaled%20Mashal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMashal%20is%20a%20founding%20member%20of%20Hamas%20Politburo%20and%20was%20the%20chairman%20until%202017.%20His%20current%20whereabouts%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20in%20Qatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMashal%20was%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20sensational%20assassination%20attempt%20in%20Jordan%20in%201997%20when%20Mossad%20agents%2C%20posing%20as%20Canadian%20tourists%2C%20sprayed%20a%20deadly%20toxin%20into%20one%20of%20his%20ears.%20The%20Mossad%20kill-team%20was%20captured%20and%20Mashal%20fell%20into%20a%20coma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Bill%20Clinton%20had%20to%20intervene%20and%20the%20then%20Mossad%20chief%20Danny%20Yatom%20had%20to%20fly%20to%20Amman%20with%20an%20antidote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'What%20Justice%20Demands'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoav%20Gallant.%20the%20Israeli%20defence%20minister%2C%20has%20mugshots%20of%20hundreds%20of%20Hams%20fighters%20and%20commanders%20on%20a%20poster%20that%20hangs%20on%20a%20wall%20of%20his%20Tel%20Aviv%20office.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20living%20on%20borrowed%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Gallant%20said%20last%20week%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20Reut