20the%20four%20people%20-%20a%20man%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20his%20sister%2C%20and%20a%20family%20friend%20-%20being%20punched%2C%20kicked%20and%20dragged%20on%20the%20narrow%20street%20by%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20wife%20and%20I%20and%20my%20sister%20were%20dropping%20a%20friend%20home%20after%20dinner%20at%2011%20pm%20when%20two%20men%20and%20a%20woman%20approached%20us%2C%20saying%20their%20mobile%20battery%20is%20dead%2C%20and%20they%20need%20help%20to%20book%20a%20cab%20to%20Munirka%20(in%20south%20Delhi)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20man%20who%20has%20a%20black%20eye%20and%20swollen%20cheeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20agreed%20to%20help.%20While%20booking%20the%20cab%2C%20the%20man%20who%20asked%20for%20help%20started%20passing%20lewd%20comments%20against%20my%20wife%20and%20sister.%20When%20we%20objected%20to%20their%20behaviour%2C%20they%20became%20aggressive%2C%20called%20some%20eight-nine%20of%20their%20friends%20and%20started%20beating%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20man%20said%2C%20adding%20he%20has%20given%20details%20in%20the%20FIR%20that%20has%20been%20corroborated%20with%20the%20mobile%20video%20and%20CCTV%20footage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20wife%20alleged%20the%20group%20pulled%20her%20hair%2C%20kicked%20her%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20tried%20to%20drag%20her.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20I%20was%20going%20to%20die%2C%20everyone%20was%20going%20to%20die%20as%20they%20did%20not%20stop%20beating%20us%2C%20no%20one%20stopped%20them%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20woman%2C%20showing%20bruises%20on%20her%20knees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20walking%20when%20they%20asked%20for%20help%20to%20book%20a%20cab%2C%20and%20this%20is%20what%20they%20have%20done%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20and%20broke%20down%20in%20front%20of%20the%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20CCTV%20grab%20of%20some%20of%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20Sunlight%20Colony%20assault%20case%20in%20Delhi%2