tensive%20work%20over%20the%20years%20to%20maintain%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20tower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20the%20tower%20is%20leaning%20excessively%20and%20has%20forced%20city%20officials%20to%20bring%20into%20action%20a%20civil%20protection%20plan.%20According%20to%20CNN%2C%20the%20tower%20is%20at%20risk%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bsudden%20and%20unexpected%20collapse%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20metal%20cordon%20will%20now%20be%20put%20up%20around%20the%20tower%20to%20contain%20the%20debris%20and%20reduce%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20surrounding%20buildings%20in%20case%20of%20a%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20protective%20cordon%20will%20be%20erected%20to%20contain%20debris%20resulting%20from%20a%20possible%20collapse%2C%20to%20reduce%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20surrounding%20buildings%20and%20the%20exposure%20to%20the%20population%2C%20as%20well%20as%20blocking%20access%20to%20the%20off-limits%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20city%20council%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20warning%20was%20issued%20by%20a%20scientific%20committee%20which%20has%20monitored%20the%20site%20since%202019.%20They%20have%20installed%20sensors%20that%20measure%20the%20movements%20of%20the%20ancient%20tower.%20The%20committee%20said%20that%20the%20readings%20in%20October%202023%20triggered%20alarm%20bells%2C%20reports%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'high%20alert'%20warning%20states%20that%20an%20%26quot%3Bunexpected%20and%20accelerated%20trend%26quot%3B%20of%20%26quot%3Bcrushing%20compression%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20base%20tower%20has%20been%20observed.%20It%20adds%20that%20the%20cracks%20in%20the%20stones%20used%20in%20the%20base%20could%20expand%20to%20the%20bricks%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20the%20report%20came%20out%2C%20civic%20officials%20shut%20down%20the%20area%20around%20the%20tower%20and%20closed%20all%20roads%20leading%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701500580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3