alk%20the%20same%20path%20without%20the%20slightest%20hint%20of%20introspection%2C%20makes%20the%20discourse%20around%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKabir%20Singh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20seem%20like%20white%20noise%20for%20the%20director.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClearly%2C%20he%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20budged%20since%20then.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02105725%2FScreenshot-2023-12-02-at-10.50.44-AM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02105725%2FScreenshot-2023-12-02-at-10.50.44-AM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02105725%2FScreenshot-2023-12-02-at-10.50.44-AM-300x125.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02105725%2FScreenshot-2023-12-02-at-10.50.44-AM-1024x427.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687351%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERanbir%20Kapoor%20in%20Animal.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20from%20video%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAnimal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20his%20protagonist%20is%20a%20scion%20of%20a%20fractured%20industrialist%20Punjabi%20family.%20Herein%20lies%2C%20Reddy%20Vanga%E2%80%99s%20masterstroke%20%E2%80%93%20the%20casting%20of%20Ranbir%20Kapoor.%20Who%20else%20in%20Bollywood%20*looks*%20the%20part%20of%20blue-blooded%20scion%2C%20better%20than%20Kapoor%3F%20Also%2C%20how%20many%20among%20the%20current%20crop%20can%20play%20the%20directionless%20lad%2C%20who%20has%20just%20returned%20from%20America%2FLondon%2C%20with%20that%20stunning%20Michael%20Corleone%20energy%2C%20and%20still%20explore%20a%20new%20facet%3F%20Kapoor%2C%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20actor-stars%20of%20his%20generation%2C%20also%20desperate%20for%20a%20blockbuster%2C%20embraces%20the%20crudeness%20of%20Reddy%20Vanga%E2%80%99s%20world%20without%20much%20ado.%20He%E2%80%99s%20the%20reluctant%20heir%20to%20a%20steel%20manufacturing%20entity%20called%20Swastik%20steel%20%E2%80%93%20whose%20symbol%20is%2C%20you%20guessed%20it%2C%20a%20Swastika.%20Not%20the%20Nazi%20kind%2C%20the%20film%20insists.%20Even%20though%20there%20are%20stray%20mentions%20to%20someone%E2%80%99s%20gene%20pool%2C%20stronger%20genes%20and%20breeding%20during%20the%20film.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERannvijay%20Singh%20says%20the%20darnedest%20things.%20%E2%80%9CLove%2C%20poetry%20and%20pining%20was%20invented%20by%20the%20non-alphas%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20tells%20Geetanjali%20(Mandanna)%20while%20trying%20to%20court%20her.%20Ten%20minutes%20later%2C%20he%20also%20goes%20on%20to%20say%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20a%20big%20pelvis%2C%20you%20can%20accommodate%20healthy%20babies.%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20their%20first%20meeting%3B%20in%20case%20you%E2%80%99re%20wondering.%20After%20almost%20killing%20six%20boys%20who%20bullied%20his%20sister%20in%20college%2C%20Rannvijay%20defends%20himself%20in%20front%20of%20his%20father%2C%20%E2%80%9CPapa%2C%20forget%20law%20and%20order%20for%20five%20minutes%E2%80%A6%20do%20you%20think%20what%20I%20did%20was%20wrong%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Ftiger-3-salman-khan-shahrukh-katrina-kaif%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Tiger%203%E2%80%99%3A%20The%20Swagger%20is%20There%2C%20But%20a%20Jaded%20Salman%20Khan%20Has%20Little%20Else%20to%20Show%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20almost%20like%20Reddy%20Vanga%20(with%20brother%20Pranay%20Reddy%20Vanga%20and%20Saurabh%20Gupta)%20has%20specifically%20written%20these%20lines%20to%20bait%20critics.%20There%E2%80%99s%20an%20entire%20scene%20between%20Rannvijay%20and%20Geetanjali%20%E2%80%93%20where%20they%20talk%20about%20their%20first%20kiss%2C%20the%20first%20time%20they%20had%20sex%2C%20so%20it%20was%20only%20natural%20their%20next%20level%20of%20intimacy%20would%20be%E2%80%A6%20the%20first%20slap.%20He%E2%80%99s%20obviously%20written%20this%20into%20the%20film%2C%20to%20spark%20think%20pieces%20about%20the%20film.%20To%20all%20those%20considering%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20worth%20it.%20This%20man%20is%20quite%20singularly%20obstinate%20%E2%80%93%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20care%20about%20critical%20feedback%2C%20because%20he%E2%80%99s%20obviously%20touched%20a%20nerve%20somewhere.%20Both%20his%20films%20have%20been%20widely%20accepted%20by%20the%20public%2C%20so%20then%20why%20should%20he%20listen%20to%20a%20few%20dozen%20voices%20cautioning%20him%20against%20his%20natural%20%E2%80%98style%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scope%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAnimal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20Shakespearean%3A%20warring%20brothers%2C%20a%20permanently%20damaged%20father-son%20bond%2C%20men%20so%20consumed%20by%20revenge%20that%20they%E2%80%99re%20willing%20to%20wait%20for%20months%2C%20years%2C%20decades%20before%20striking%20back.%20This%20could%E2%80%99ve%20been%20a%20focused%20action%20film%20about%20violence%20being%20inherited%20from%20one%20generation%20to%20the%20next%3B%20akin%20to%20Park%20Hoon-jung%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENew%20World%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2013).%20But%20with%20Reddy%20Vanga%E2%80%99s%20empty%20provocation%2C%20and%20his%20tendency%20to%20overwrite%20a%20scene%20with%20thoughts%20and%20opinions%20that%20feel%20borrowed%20from%20an%20incel%20treatise%20%E2%80%93%20the%20little%20potential%20it%20could%20have%20had%20is%20lost%20over%20several%20long%20drawn-out%20sequences.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02105826%2FScreenshot-2023-12-02-at-10.49.46-AM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02105826%2FScreenshot-2023-12-02-at-10.49.46-AM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02105826%2FScreenshot-2023-12-02-at-10.49.46-AM-300x163.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02105826%2FScreenshot-2023-12-02-at-10.49.46-AM-1024x557.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687352%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22653%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAnil%20Kapoor%20in%20Animal.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20from%20video%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETycoon%20Balbir%20Singh%20(Anil%20Kapoor%20doing%20his%20best%20Logan%20Roy%20impression)%20survives%20an%20assassination%20attempt%2C%20causing%20Rannvijay%20to%20take%20over%20the%20reins%20of%20business%20and%20find%20the%20culprit.%20Even%20with%20all%20the%20money%20in%20the%20world%2C%20the%20Singhs%20are%20obviously%20not%20well-acquainted%20with%20the%20boons%20of%20a%20strong%20information%20network.%20Which%20is%20why%20they%20go%20through%20the%20preposterous%20method%20of%20creating%20body%20doubles%20to%20lure%20out%20perpetrators.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20pre-interval%20corridor%20scene%20that%20seems%20inspired%20from%20Park%20Chan-wook%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EOldboy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2003)%20and%20an%20gargantuan%20Maxim%20machine%20gun%20sequence%2C%20which%20seems%20like%20a%20by-product%20of%20Lokesh%20Kannagraj%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVikram%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2022).%20The%20corridor%20scene%20has%20none%20of%20the%20