lled%20on%20all%20nations%20to%20fulfill%20their%20climate%20targets.%20He%20also%20introduced%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CGreen%20Credit%20Initiative%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20world%2C%20and%20launched%20it%20at%20the%20High-Level%20Event%20on%20the%20Green%20Credit%20Initiative%20later%20in%20the%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Balance%20between%20ecology%20and%20economy%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20fact%20that%20India%20is%20home%20to%2017%25%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20our%20share%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20carbon%20emissions%20is%20less%20than%204%25%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20while%20speaking%20at%20the%20ceremonial%20opening%20of%20the%20High-Level%20Segment%20for%20national%20statements%20on%20the%20second%20day%20of%20COP28%20in%20Dubai%2C%20UAE.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20past%20century%2C%20a%20small%20section%20of%20humanity%20has%20indiscriminately%20exploited%20nature%2C%20however%2C%20entire%20humanity%20is%20paying%20the%20price%20for%20this%2C%20especially%20people%20living%20in%20the%20Global%20South%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20give%20all%20developing%20countries%20a%20fair%20share%20in%20the%20global%20carbon%20budget%2C%20we%20have%20to%20be%20more%20balanced%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20A%20balance%20must%20be%20struck%20between%20adaptation%2C%20mitigation%2C%20climate%20finance%2C%20technology%2C%20as%20well%20as%20loss%20and%20damage%2C%20he%20added.%20Moreover%2C%20energy%20transitions%20must%20be%20just%2C%20inclusive%20and%20equitable.%20He%20urged%20that%20every%20country%20fulfill%20its%20climate%20targets.%20Modi%20also%20offered%20that%20India%20would%20host%20the%2033rd%20COP%20in%202028.%20India%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20countries%20that%20was%20on%20track%20to%20achieve%20all%20its%20Nationally%20Determined%20Contributions%20before%20time%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20has%20also%20presented%20%E2%80%9Ca%20model%20of%20development%20to%20the%20world%20by%20striking%20a%20great%20balance%20between%20ecology%20and%20economy%E2%80%9D%2C%20Modi%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20former%20environmental%20minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20commented%20that%20Modi%20followed%20the%20%E2%80%9CMaximum%20Global%20Talk%2C%20Minimum%20Local%20Walk%E2%80%9D%20in%20his%20speech.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20India%20has%20%E2%80%9Cstruck%20a%20great%20balance%20between%20ecology%20and%20economy%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9Cyet%20another%20of%20his%20trademark%20falsehoods%E2%80%9D%2C%20Ramesh%20said%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1730561850146750703%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20tweeted%20on%20December%201.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reality%20is%20that%20several%20legislations%20to%20protect%20the%20environment%20have%20been%20diluted%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20Ramesh%20said.%20The%20Forest%20Conservation%20Act%201980%20%E2%80%9Chas%20been%20made%20completely%20hollow%20with%20a%202023%20amendment%E2%80%9D%20and%20this%20removes%20protection%20for%2025%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20forest%20cover%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20the%201996%20TN%20Godavarman%20Supreme%20Court%20order%2C%20apart%20from%20doing%20away%20with%20the%20consent%20of%20forest%20communities%2C%20and%20with%20requirements%20for%20forest%20clearance%20in%20vast%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20Modi%20Government%20to%20exploit%20forests%20and%20hand%20them%20over%20to%20a%20select%20few%20chosen%20corporates%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%20of%202006%20was%20weakened%20with%20a%20notification%20in%202022%20and%20that%20forests%20can%20now%20be%20cleared%20without%20consulting%20those%20who%20live%20there.%20Consent%20from%20gram%20sabhas%20is%20no%20longer%20needed%20to%20use%20forest%20land%2C%20he%20said.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20National%20Biodiversity%20Act%20of%202002%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Cmassively%20diluted%E2%80%9D%20to%20allow%20private%20companies%20easier%20access%20to%20forests%20without%20benefit-sharing%20with%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20National%20Biodiversity%20Authority%20(NBA)%2C%20formerly%20an%20independent%20body%20able%20to%20keep%20a%20check%20on%20the%20government%2C%20has%20been%20completely%20put%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20Environment%20Ministry%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramesh%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F10143411%2FInto-the-forest-scenery-Gorumara-forest-India-86509-pixahive-1024x631-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F10143411%2FInto-the-forest-scenery-Gorumara-forest-India-86509-pixahive-1024x631-1.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F10143411%2FInto-the-forest-scenery-Gorumara-forest-India-86509-pixahive-1024x631-1-300x185.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-606748%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22631%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Roy%2FPixahive%2C%20CC0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20passed%2039%20amendments%20to%20rules%20under%20the%20Environment%20Protection%20Act%3B%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20has%20been%20weakened%20since%202014%20as%20have%20Environmental%20Impact%20Assessment%20norms%20since%202020%2C%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTimelines%20for%20hydro%20and%20mining%20project%20clearances%20have%20been%20arbitrarily%20extended%2C%20major%20project%20types%20have%20been%20removed%20from%20central%20government%20clearance%2C%20public%20hearings%20and%20participation%20have%20been%20skipped.%20In%20eco-sensitive%20areas%20like%20the%20Himalayan%20region%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20illegally%20bypassed%20the%20need%20for%20Environmental%20Impact%20Assessment%20by%20splitting%20large%20projects%20into%20small%20segments.%20The%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20disaster%20is%20only%20a%20symptom%20of%20the%20larger%20malaise.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAir%20pollution%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgrave%20public%20health%20crisis%E2%80%9D%20under%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20becoming%20a%20major%20threat%20to%20life%20expectancy%2C%20Ramesh%20also%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%202015%20to%202020%20alone%2C%20the%20share%20of%20Indians%20exposed%20to%20PM2.5%20above%20100%20has%20doubled%2C%20reversing%20improvements%20over%20the%20previous%20years.%20The%20Modi%20government%20has%20not%20only%20been%20ineffective%20in%20dealing%20with%20worsening%20air%20pollution%20across%20the%20country%2C%20but%20it%20relaxed%20norms%20for%20coal%20transportation%20and%20emissions%20scrubbing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20anyone%20take%20what%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20says%20globally%20on%20%5Bthe%5D%20environment%20seriously%20in%20light%20of%20his%20disastrous%20track%20record%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramesh%20asked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EGreen%20Credit%20Initiative%20launched%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20in%20his%20speech%20at%20the%20ceremonial%20opening%20of%20the%20High-Level%20Segment%20for%20national%20statements%20on%20December%201%20also%20introduced%20the%20Green%20Credit%20Initiative%20to%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Green%20Credit%20Initiative%20is%20based%20on%20the%20national%20Green%20Credit%20Programme%20that%20India%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1967476%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elaunched%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20October%20this%20year.%20Per%20the%20Programme%2C%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Can%20innovative%20market-based%20mechanism%20designed%20to%20incentivize%20voluntary%20environmental%20actions%20across%20diverse%20sectors%2C%20by%20various%20stakeholders%20like%20individuals%2C%20communities%2C%20private%20sector%20industries%2C%20and%20companies%E2%80%9D.%20The%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20GCP%20aims%20to%20focus%20on%20water%20conservation%20and%20afforestation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20a%20new%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1981719%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20also%20listed%20by%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37320%2FIndia_cohosts_with_UAE_the_Global_Green_Credit_Initiative_at_COP28%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMinistry%20of%20External%20Affairs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20global%20Green%20Credit%20Initiative%20%E2%80%9Chas%20been%20conceptualised%20as%20a%20mechanism%20to%20incentivize%20voluntary%20pro-planet%20actions%E2%80%9D%20to%20tackle%20climate%20change.%20Per%20the%20Ministry%2C%20the%20Initiative%20will%20issue%20%E2%80%9CGreen%20Credits%E2%80%9D%20for%20plantations%20on%20waste%2Fdegraded%20lands%20and%20river%20catchment%20areas%2C%20%E2%80%9Cto%20rejuvenate%20and%20revive%20natural%20ecosystems%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20launched%20the%20global%20Green%20Credit%20Initiative%20at%20a%20high-level%20event%20after%20the%20opening%20ceremony%20of%20the%20High-Level%20Segment%20on%20December%201.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20has%20always%20felt%20that%20the%20scope%20of%20carbon%20credits%20is%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20limited%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20this%20philosophy%20is%20%E2%80%9Cfilled%20with%20commercial%20elements%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRegarding%20carbon%20credits%2C%20I%20see%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20social%20responsibility.%20We%20should%20lean%20on%20new%20philosophy%20in%20a%20holistic%20way.%20And%20this%20is%20the%20mark%20of%20green%20credit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20we%20sacrifice%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evikruti%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20or%20destruction%2C%20and%20think%20that%20only%20if%20we%20advance%20the%20environment%20can%20we%20advance%20ourselves%2C%20only%20then%20can%20we%20save%20the%20environment%2C%20he%20said%2C%20likening%20the%20system%20to%20health%20cards.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20like%20we%20update%20our%20health%20cards%E2%80%A6we%20need%20to%20think%20of%20our%20environment%20too.%20We%20need%20to%20see%20what%20we%20can%20do%20to%20increase%20the%20positive%20points%20in%20the%20health%20card%20of%20the%20earth.%20This%20in%20my%20opinion%20is%20%E2%80%9Cgreen%20credit%E2%80%9D.%20That%20is%20my%20concept%20of%20green%20credits.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20green%20credit%20will%20be%20useful%20in%20future%20expansion%20and%20is%20tradable%20as%20well.%20The%20entire%20process%20will%20be%20fully%20digital%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%20is%20registration%2C%20plantation%20or%20verification%2C%20or%20to%20initiate%20green%20credit%E2%80%A6We%20have%20to%20work%20together%20on%20several%20such%20ideas.%20So%20we%20are%20also%20launching%20a%20global%20platform.%20This%20portal%20will%20collect%20all%20ideas%2C%20expressions%20and%20innovations%20linked%20to%20plantation%20and%20the%20environment%20in%20one%20area.%20This%20repository%20will%20help%20shape%20the%20policies%2C%20practices%20and%20global%20demand%20in%20green%20credits.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20saying%20that%20nature%20protects%20those%20who%20protect%20them.%20Using%20this%20initiative%20I%20implore%20that%20for%20this%20earth%2C%20for%20our%20future%2C%20we%20build%20a%20cleaner%2C%20greener%20and%20better%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWill%20the%20Green%20Credit%20system%20really%20be%20green%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20think%20in%20terms%20of%20laws%20and%20actions%20about%20how%20we%20can%20merge%20green%20credit%20with%20the%20earth%E2%80%99s%20health%20card%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20added%2C%20about%20the%20Green%20Credit%20Initiative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20degraded%20wastelands.%20If%20we%20go%20by%20the%20concept%20of%20green%20credits%2C%20first%20we%20make%20an%20inventory%20of%20these%20degraded%20wastelands.%20Then%20any%20individual%20or%20organization%20will%20use%20these%20for%20%E2%80%9Cvoluntary%20plantations%E2%80%9D.%20And%20for%20this%20%E2%80%9Cpositive%20action%E2%80%9D%2C%20that%20individual%20or%20organization%20will%20be%20given%20a%20green%20credit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Csmall%20example%E2%80%9D%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdegraded%20wastelands%E2%80%9D%20is%20actually%20not%20a%20small%20one%20at%20all.%20Large%20tracts%20of%20lands%20classified%20as%20%E2%80%9Cwastelands%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20are%20highly%20productive%20and%20important%20natural%20ecosystems%2C%20often%20called%20Open%20Natural%20Ecosystems%2C%20and%20include%20savannas.%20Afforestation%20in%20such%20landscapes%20can%20be%20detrimental%2C%20scientists%20have%20found.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20considering%20%E2%80%9Cdegraded%20wastelands%E2%80%9D%20for%20restoration%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20many%20of%20these%20are%20savanna%20grasslands%20and%20other%20Open%20Natural%20Ecosystems%20that%20have%20been%20wrongly%20classified%20as%20wastelands%2C%20Abi%20Tamim%20Vanak%2C%20Director%2C%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Design%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESenior%20Fellow%20at%20the%20Ashoka%20Trust%20for%20Research%20in%20Ecology%20and%20the%20Environment%20(ATREE)%2C%20Bangalore%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20crucial%20that%20ecological%20restoration%20keeps%20the%20original%20ecosystem%20in%20mind%2C%20and%20we%20do%20not%20indulge%20in%20only%20tree%20plantation%20programs%20that%20are%20likely%20to%20damage%20these%20fragile%20ecosystems%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Tree%20plantations%20in%20such%20areas%20may%20actually%20result%20in%20loss%20of%20below-ground%20carbon%2C%20reduce%20groundwater%20recharge%20and%20negatively%20affect%20pastoralist%20livelihoods%20and%20endanger%20biodiversity%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20November%2C%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbesjournals.onlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1111%2F1365-2745.14221%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estudy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20a%20team%20of%20researchers%20including%20Ashish%20Nerlekar%2C%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Ecology%20and%20Conservation%20Biology%2C%20Texas%20A%26amp%3BM%20University%2C%20found%20that%20converting%20old-growth%20savannas%20into%20agricultural%20tracts%20and%20afforesting%20them%20destroys%20and%20degrades%20the%20smaller%2C%20herbaceous%20plant%20communities%20that%20do%20not%20spontaneously%20recover%20on%20fallowed%20land.%20The%20team%20studied%20savannas%20in%20western%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlanting%20trees%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20savannas%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20restoration%20is%20detrimental%20to%20native%20and%20endemic%20plants%2C%20commented%20Nerlekar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20study%20shows%20that%20on%20average%2C%20planting%20trees%20on%20savannas%20results%20in%20a%20loss%20of%204%20native%20herbaceous%20plants%20per%20sq.%20meter%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20show%20that%20the%20magnitude%20of%20these%20losses%20also%20depends%20on%20the%20kinds%20of%20savannas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%20%E2%80%9CPlanting%20trees%20on%20mesic%20or%20wetter%20savannas%20is%20much%20more%20harmful%20than%20planting%20on%20drier%20or%20semi%20arid%20savannas.%20Much%20of%20India%20happens%20to%20be%20mesic%20savannas%20so%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%5Bthe%20Green%20Credit%20Initiative%20for%20%E2%80%9Cdegraded%20wastelands%E2%80%9D%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20certainly%20bad%20news.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EGaza%20in%20the%20spotlight%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECOP28%20president%20Sultan%20Ahmed%20Al-Jaber%20said%20in%20his%20opening%20remarks%20at%20the%20high%20level%20segment%20ceremony%20that%20they%20had%20%E2%80%9Ccollectively%20made%20history%E2%80%9D%20yesterday%20by%20operationalising%20the%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20Fund.%20Over%20170%20heads%20of%20state%20and%20governments%20will%20deliver%20their%20national%20statements%20at%20COP28%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25123525%2FF9O1QYgbQAARmyY.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25123525%2FF9O1QYgbQAARmyY.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25123525%2FF9O1QYgbQAARmyY-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25123525%2FF9O1QYgbQAARmyY-1024x678.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681609%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22794%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGaza.%20Photo%3AX%2F%40MofaPPD%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20war%20and%20civilian%20deaths%20in%20Gaza%20in%20Palestine%20came%20under%20focus%20as%20several%20heads%20of%20states%20and%20governments%20mentioned%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20war%20which%20is%20ongoing%20in%20the%20Arabian%20continent%20even%20as%20COP28%20progresses%2C%20while%20delivering%20their%20national%20statements.%20Fresh%20firing%20has%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fcop28-climate-summit-israel-palestinians-hamas-war-b2ded089961f96d05bb2f171131e8cf6%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20Gaza%20strip%20over%20the%20last%20two%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJordan%E2%80%99s%20King%20Abdullah%20said%20while%20delivering%20his%20country%E2%80%99s%20national%20statement%20that%20Jordan%20had%20initiated%20a%20food%20security%20programme%20and%20will%20deal%20with%20war%20refugees.%20He%20said%20that%20war%20was%20making%20the%20threats%20from%20climate%20change%20even%20worse%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Gaza%2C%20over%201.7%20million%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20displaced%20from%20their%20homes.%20Tens%20of%20thousands%20have%20been%20injured%20or%20killed%20in%20a%20region%20already%20on%20the%20front%20lines%20of%20climate%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barrons.com%2Fnews%2Fgaza-war-worsening-climate-change-threats-says-jordan-s-king-d9440dba%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESerbian%20president%20Aleksandar%20Vucic%20asked%20how%20we%20can%20find%20solutions%20to%20climate%20change%20if%20we%20cannot%20find%20solutions%20to%20geopolitical%20issues%20that%20threaten%20territories%20now.%20According%20to%20one%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2Finteractive%2F2023%2Fgaza-rising-death-toll-civilians%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eestimate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20more%20than%2011%2C100%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20since%20October%207%2C%20as%20per%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20Health%20Ministry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20expressing%20here%20our%20views%20on%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20not%20talk%20about%20the%20humanitarian%20crisis%20taking%20place%20in%20Palestinian%20territories%20close%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Turkish%20president%20Recep%20Erdogan.%20More%20than%2016%2C000%20civilians%2C%20mostly%20women%20and%20children%2C%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20aggression%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20cannot%20be%20justified%20under%20any%20circumstances.%20The%20incidents%20taking%20place%20in%20Gaza%20are%20a%20humanitarian%20crime%2C%20a%20war%20crime%20and%20the%20perpetrators%20must%20be%20held%20accountable%20before%20international%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHadeel%20Ikhmais%2C%20a%20climate%20change%20expert%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fcop28-climate-summit-israel-palestinians-hamas-war-b2ded089961f96d05bb2f171131e8cf6%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20AP%20about%20the%20deaths%20seen%20by%20Palestinians%2C%20both%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20the%20West%2