iwari%20and%20his%20team%20intimidated%20and%20received%20bribes%20from%20several%20persons%20in%C2%A0exchange%C2%A0of%20dropping%20charges%20against%20them%2C%20the%20police%20alleged%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftamil-nadu%2Falleged-ed-official-arrested-in-tamil-nadu-for-taking-bribes-to-close-cases%5C%22%3Eas%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%20This%20alleged%20bribery%20racket%20was%20discovered%20months%20after%20ED%20raids%20on%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20leaders%20and%20their%20associates.%20Former%20minister%20for%20Electricity%2C%20Prohibition%2C%20and%20Excise%20V.%20Senthil%20Balaji%20was%20arrested%20earlier%20this%20year%20by%20ED%20for%20his%20cash-for-jobs%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%20that%20Tiwari%20is%20a%202016-batch%20officer%2C%20who%20had%20previously%20served%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Ftamil-nadu-police-arrest-senior-ed-officer-for-accepting-bribe-of-rs-20-lakh-9050047%2F%5C%22%3Eis%20currently%20posted%20in%20Madurai.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20Higher%20Education%20Minister%20K%20Ponmudi%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20Villupuram%20was%20also%20raided%20by%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20this%20year%2C%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Anti-Corruption%20Bureau%20(ACB)%20arrested%20two%20ED%20officials%20on%20bribery%20charges%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20agency%20issued%20summons%20to%20the%20sons%20of%20the%20state%20Congress%20Committee%20Chief%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasra.%20Dotasra%E2%80%99s%20sons%2C%20Abhilash%20and%20Avinash%2C%20had%20been%20summoned%20by%20the%20ED%20with%20reference%20to%20an%20alleged%20exam%20paper%20leak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20DMK-led%20state%20government%20had%20moved%20the%20Madras%20high%20court%20against%20ED%20summons%20to%2010%20district%20collectors%20as%20part%20of%20an%20investigation%20into%20alleged%20irregularities%20and%20malpractices%20in%20the%20mining%20and%20sale%20of%20river%20sand%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20high%20court%20had%20stayed%20the%20summons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20controversy%20regarding%20action%20by%20state%20police%20on%20central%20agency%20officers%20goes%2C%20there%20is%20a%20view%20that%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Vigilance%20and%20Anti-Corruption%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20%E2%80%9Cwell%20within%20its%20jurisdiction%20to%20arrest%20an%20ED%20officer%20(Central%20Govt%20employee)%20on%20bribery%20allegations.%20With%20the%20State%20Govt%20revoking%20General%20Consent%20to%20CBI%20under%20Sec%206%20of%20DSPE%20Act%2C%20State%20Police%20has%20sole%20jurisdiction%20over%20Central%20Govt%20employees%20too%20in%20its%20territory%20under%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20high%20court%20in%20a%20judgement%20this%20year%20ruled%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20special%20provision%20in%20the%20P.C%20Act%20or%20DSPE%20Act%20excluding%20or%20preventing%20the%20State%20police%20or%20a%20Special%20Agency%20of%20the%20State%20from%20investigating%20cases%20relating%20to%20the%20corruption%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%20employees.%20None%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20P.C%20Act%20or%20DSPE%20Act%20authorises%20CBI%20or%20Central%20Vigilance%20Commission%20or%20any%20other%20Central%20Government%20Agency%20alone%20to%20investigate%20in%20matters%20relating%20to%20the%20Central%20Government%20employees%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EKerala%20HC%20in%20a%202023%20judgment%20has%20held%20as%20follows%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20special%20provision%20in%20the%20P.C%20Act%20or%20DSPE%20Act%20excluding%20or%20preventing%20the%20State%20police%20or%20a%20Special%20Agency%20of%20the%20State%20from%20investigating%20cases%20relating%2