ram%20will%20be%20held%20on%20Monday%20(December%204)%2C%20instead%20of%20Sunday%20(December%203)%20as%20notified%20earlier%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20EC%2C%20the%20change%20is%20in%20response%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Eseveral%20representations%20from%20various%20quarters%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Commission%20has%20received%20several%20representations%20from%20various%20quarters%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Erequesting%20for%20change%20in%20the%20date%20of%20counting%20from%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%20December%203%2C%202023%20(Sunday)%20to%20some%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Eother%20week%20day%2C%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDecember%203%2C%202023%2C%20being%20Sunday%20a%20special%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Esignificance%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Mizoram%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20EC%20statement%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20in%20the%20counting%20date%20will%20not%20affect%20other%20states%20where%20elections%20concluded%20recently.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20take%20place%20on%20December%203%2C%20as%20announced%20earlier%2C%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fmizoram-churches-pray-change-counting-date-assembly-polls%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20that%20churches%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20on%20Sunday%2C%20November%2026%2C%20held%20special%20prayers%20to%20seek%20%E2%80%9Cdivine%20intervention%E2%80%9D%20to%20help%20in%20their%20efforts%20to%20persuade%20the%20poll%20body%20to%20reschedule%20the%20counting%20date.%20Being%20a%20Christian-majority%20state%2C%20Mizoram%20considers%20Sunday%20solely%2