2https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28154925%2Fimage-1445.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20More%20than%20400%20signatories%2C%20including%20sociologists%2C%20political%20scientists%2C%20academicians%2C%20researchers%2C%20and%20journalists%2C%20have%20expressed%20outrage%20against%20at%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20discussions%20on%20the%20ongoing%20war%20against%20Palestine%20are%20being%20silenced%20on%20Indian%20campuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20issuing%20this%20statement%20to%20call%20upon%20university%20administrators%20and%20the%20government%20to%20respect%20our%20academic%20freedom.%20We%20would%20also%20like%20to%20remind%20everyone%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20own%20long%20history%20of%20anti-colonial%20struggle%20which%20has%20historically%20provided%20the%20lens%20through%20which%20the%20Palestinian%20struggle%20for%20self-determination%2C%20equality%20and%20human%20rights%20has%20been%20viewed%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20object%20to%20the%20way%20in%20which%20any%20discussion%20of%20the%20historical%20context%20of%20the%20occupation%20of%20Palestine%20and%20the%20barbaric%20Israeli%20assault%20on%20Gaza%2C%20along%20with%20the%20denial%20of%20food%2C%20fuel%20and%20water%2C%20since%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20is%20being%20projected%20as%20support%20for%20the%20brutal%20terror%20attack%20on%20civilians%20in%20Israel%20by%20Hamas%20on%20October%207%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20object%20to%20the%20Israeli%20ambassador%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legallyindia.com%2Fconvos%2Ftopic%2F303502-breaking-news-israeli-ambassador-to-india-had-complained-to-jindal-vc-about-sameena-dalwai-and-palestine-event-reveals-scroll-also-gives-gives-inside-story-on-bumble-gate%5C%22%3Einterference%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20academic%20freedom%20on%20Indian%20campuses.%20This%20disrespects%20the%20competence%20of%20Indian%20scholars%20to%20analyse%20historical%20and%20political%20situations%20for%20themselves.%20Defending%20the%20right%20to%20life%20and%20dignity%20of%20Palestinians%2C%20or%20pointing%20out%20the%20links%20between%20Zionism%20and%20Hindutva%20as%20supremacist%20ideologies%2C%20is%20not%20equivalent%20to%20antisemitism%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20in%20reference%20to%20former%20Delhi%20University%20professor%20Achin%20Vanaik%E2%80%99s%20recent%20lecture%20on%20Palestine%20at%20O.P.%20Jindal%20University.%20Although%20the%20university%20had%20asked%20Vanaik%20to%20%E2%80%9Cexpress%20regret%E2%80%9D%20over%20his%20remark%2C%20the%20professor%20said%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fasked-by-o-p-jindal-university-to-express-regret-achin-vanaik-stands-by-lecture-on-palestine%5C%22%3Estands%20by%20his%20lecture.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Vanaik%E2%80%99s%20lecture%20on%20November%201%2C%20the%20Israeli%20Ambassador%20to%20India%20Naor%20Gilon%2C%20wrote%20to%20the%20founding%20vice-chancellor%20of%20the%20university%2C%20Prof.%20C.%20Raj%20Kumar%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fscholar-stands-by-his-lecture-at-op-jindal-university-regrets-its-misinterpretation%2Farticle67551383.ece%5C%22%3Esaying%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20understand%20why%20an%20event%20delegitimizsng%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20was%20hosted%20at%20the%20University.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20also%20strongly%20condemns%20the%20appropriation%20of%20the%20Palestine%20issue%20to%20fuel%20Islamophobia%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20all%20the%20attacks%20on%20campus%20events%20on%20Palestine%2C%20we%20see%20the%20Hindutva%20ecosystem%20at%20work%20%E2%80%93%20known%20Hindutva%20individuals%20who%20tweet%20against%20the%20faculty%20members%20concerned%2C%20groups%20which%20organise%20protests%20against%20them%20on%20campus%2C%20and%20a%20pliant%20media%20which%20engages%20in%20defamation%20of%20the%20academics%20as%20terror%20supporters%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20urges%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20political%20parties%20to%20cease%20criminalizing%20solidarity%20protests%20with%20Palestine%2C%20citing%20examples%20of%20FIRs%20against%20students%20and%20detentions%20in%20various%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20opposition%20parties%20have%20failed%20to%20show%20sufficient%20solidarity%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Palestine%20and%20have%20thus%20betrayed%20the%20history%20of%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndia%E2%80%99s%20own%20freedom%20struggle%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20calls%20on%20university%20administrations%20to%20uphold%20their%20statutory%20and%20constitutional%20obligations%2C%20respecting%20the%20rights%20of%20faculty%20and%20students%20to%20organize%20talks%20and%20invite%20speakers%20without%20interference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20full%20statement%2C%20with%20the%20names%20of%20the%20signatories%2C%20is%20reproduced%20below.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStatement%20of%20Solidarity%20with%20Palestine%20and%20Condemnation%20of%20Attacks%20on%20Academic%20Freedom%20Related%20to%20Palestine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20academics%20and%20other%20concerned%20persons%2C%20we%2C%20the%20undersigned%2C%20are%20outraged%20at%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20discussions%20on%20the%20ongoing%20war%20against%20Palestine%20are%20being%20silenced%20on%20Indian%20campuses%2C%20and%20in%20the%20public%20sphere%20more%20broadly.%20We%20are%20issuing%20this%20statement%20to%20call%20upon%20university%20administrators%20and%20the%20government%20to%20respect%20our%20academic%20freedom.%20We%20would%20also%20like%20to%20remind%20everyone%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20own%20long%20history%20of%20anti-colonial%20struggle%20which%20has%20historically%20provided%20the%20lens%20through%20which%20the%20Palestinian%20struggle%20for%20self-determination%2C%20equality%20and%20human%20rights%20has%20been%20viewed%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20object%20to%20the%20way%20in%20which%20any%20discussion%20of%20the%20historical%20context%20of%20the%20occupation%20of%20Palestine%20and%20the%20barbaric%20Israeli%20assault%20on%20Gaza%2C%20along%20with%20the%20denial%20of%20food%2C%20fuel%20and%20water%2C%20since%20October%207th%202023%2C%20is%20being%20projected%20as%20support%20for%20the%20brutal%20terror%20attack%20on%20civilians%20in%20Israel%20by%20Hamas%20on%20October%207th.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20object%20to%20the%20Israeli%20ambassador%E2%80%99s%20interference%20with%20academic%20freedom%20on%20Indian%20campuses.%20This%20disrespects%20the%20competence%20of%20Indian%20scholars%20to%20analyze%20historical%20and%20political%20situations%20for%20themselves.%20Defending%20the%20right%20to%20life%20and%20dignity%20of%20Palestinians%2C%20or%20pointing%20out%20the%20links%20between%20Zionism%20and%20Hindutva%20as%20supremacist%20ideologies%2C%20is%20not%20equivalent%20to%20antisemitism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20hijacking%20of%20the%20Palestine%20issue%20to%20further%20Islamophobia%20within%20India.%20In%20all%20the%20attacks%20on%20campus%20events%20on%20Palestine%2C%20we%20see%20the%20Hindutva%20ecosystem%20at%20work%20%E2%80%93%20known%20Hindutva%20individuals%20who%20tweet%20against%20the%20faculty%20members%20concerned%2C%20groups%20which%20organize%20protests%20against%20them%20on%20campus%2C%20and%20a%20pliant%20media%20which%20engages%20in%20defamation%20of%20the%20academics%20as%20terror%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20demand%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20as%20well%20as%20all%20political%20parties%20in%20power%20in%20different%20states%20stop%20criminalizing%20protests%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Palestine.%20The%20FIRs%20filed%20against%20students%20of%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20Universit