%20debris%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20Hindu%20deities%2C%20the%20Ashoka%20Chakra%2C%20786%2C%20etc%20are%20implanted%20in%20the%20oyster.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334677%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESanjay%20highlights%20that%20usually%20%E2%80%98designer%20debris%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20Hindu%20deities%2C%20the%20Ashoka%20Chakra%2C%20786%2C%20etc%20are%20implanted%20in%20the%20oyster.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaster%20the%20easier%20surgery%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20says%20that%20there%20are%20several%20types%20of%20surgical%20procedures%20in%20pearl%20cultures%20%E2%80%94%20like%20gonadal%20implantation%2C%20mantle%20tissue%20implantation%2C%20and%20mantle%20cavity%20insertion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20suggest%20that%20farmers%20learn%20mantle%20tissue%20surgery%20as%20it%20is%20easier%20to%20perform%20and%20the%20chances%20of%20oysters%20are%20higher%20as%20compared%20to%20other%20kinds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrepare%20the%20pond%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20informs%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20provide%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F267186%2Fpearl-farming-cultivation-oyster-shell-home-made-pond-set-up-ashok-manwani-kuljana%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22